{"tid":797301,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人N首口水舞嘅歌曲","createTime":"2018-08-28T11:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T04:07:28.000Z","uid":199675,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"72a42b05f0429605998e0baf4be187f524f2a502","tid":797301,"uid":199675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T11:49:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n浪花一朵朵<br />\n<br />\n詞曲 任賢齊/陳慶祥(阿牛)<br />\n<br />\n我要你陪著我　看著那海龜水中游<br />\n慢慢的爬在沙灘上　數著浪花一朵朵<br />\n你不要害怕　你不會寂寞<br />\n我會一直陪在你的左右　讓你樂悠悠<br />\n<br />\n日子一天一天過　我們會慢慢長大<br />\n我不管你懂不懂我在唱什麼<br />\n我知道有一天　你　一定會愛上我<br />\n因為我覺得我真的很不錯<br />\n<br />\n時光匆匆匆匆流走　也也也不回頭<br />\n美女變成老太婆<br />\n<br />\n哎喲　那那那個時候　我我我我也也<br />\n已經變成糟老頭<br />\n啦啦...　我們一起手牽手<br />\n啦啦...數著浪花一朵朵"},{"pid":"7665d236528cbdcd8e166e17fa6ee23bb60d1d22","tid":797301,"uid":47486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T11:50:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738a1f93878f0d1dee54f1606d10f1c4f4780369","tid":797301,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T11:50:16.000Z","msg":"《應該分開嗎》"},{"pid":"3e2ccc1d79d65a5d8d5d8f94619e7c6ef53c48b3","tid":797301,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T11:52:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/28/195224_ad33ed1f9a1534e66af332f060a430c5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F28%2F195224_ad33ed1f9a1534e66af332f060a430c5.gif&h=25748734&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8338205a867cbe373121ca33ec411ccb1f1af9c3","tid":797301,"uid":199675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"738a1f93878f0d1dee54f1606d10f1c4f4780369","tid":797301,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T11:50:16.000Z","msg":"《應該分開嗎》"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T11:54:36.000Z","msg":"吓?"},{"pid":"98d3bddab4e835f4c9907674d47ba65b6668ce77","tid":797301,"uid":199675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:07:57.000Z","msg":"王馨平 生命有價<br />\n<br />\n盡快將 憂愁眼睛<br />\n憂愁面孔 憂愁內心<br />\n拋棄吧<br />\n找回你的微笑嘴巴<br />\n一同和唱可以嗎<br />\n啦&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n一同拍掌 全力讚賞<br />\n生存是有價<br />\n<br />\n從哇哇一聲睜開眼睛看地球<br />\n從懂得緊握媽媽暖的手<br />\n到咿咿呀呀一聲兩聲仍唔夠<br />\n從爬爬行行然後曉得走<br />\n<br />\n從揹起書包吸取知識不用愁<br />\n從你有佢有開始手牽手<br />\n到他朝開心傷心痛心<br />\n齊嘗透<br />\n人活著實在奇妙怎猜透<br />\n<br />\n願你知生命實在亦是有些意外<br />\n不用徬徨迷途只須緊記<br />\n它有無窮色彩<br />\n它有無盡的愛<br />\n願憑著自信跨過障礙賽﻿"},{"pid":"48d45262dd724a43c915395b29c5e5456c580284","tid":797301,"uid":110260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T21:52:40.000Z","msg":"最撚憎口水舞"},{"pid":"bd7ec5f5435c80815c016de7e544237e809b9371","tid":797301,"uid":199675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48d45262dd724a43c915395b29c5e5456c580284","tid":797301,"uid":110260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T21:52:40.000Z","msg":"最撚憎口水舞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T03:08:48.000Z","msg":"why?"},{"pid":"45eab4c7c67a56ca77d7c36748bf17edb5457036","tid":797301,"uid":184233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:07:28.000Z","msg":"TT <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}